<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="259" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="2.[139,791,1349,1949]" pageId="2" pageNumber="259">
<emphasis box="[177,257,1349,1372]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="259">Notes. –</emphasis>
The overall morphology of the new species can be compared to: 
<taxonomicName authority="(Ridl.) Callm. &amp; Buerki" authorityName="Callm. &amp; Buerki" baseAuthorityName="Ridl." box="[285,692,1381,1405]" class="Liliopsida" family="Pandanaceae" genus="Benstonea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Pandanales" pageId="2" pageNumber="259" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="glaucophylla">
<emphasis box="[285,434,1381,1405]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="259">B. glaucophylla</emphasis>
(Ridl.) Callm. &amp; Buerki
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="(Ridl.) Callm. &amp; Buerki" authorityName="Callm. &amp; Buerki" baseAuthorityName="Ridl." class="Liliopsida" family="Pandanaceae" genus="Benstonea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Pandanales" pageId="2" pageNumber="259" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="parva">
<emphasis box="[702,790,1381,1404]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="259">B. parva</emphasis>
(Ridl.) Callm. &amp; Buerki
</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName authority="(Ridl.) Callm. &amp; Buerki. All" authorityName="Callm. &amp; Buerki. All" baseAuthorityName="Ridl." class="Liliopsida" family="Pandanaceae" genus="Benstonea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Pandanales" pageId="2" pageNumber="259" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="undulifolia">
<emphasis box="[460,602,1413,1437]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="259">B. undulifolia</emphasis>
(Ridl.) Callm. &amp; Buerki. All
</taxonomicName>
three species share wide, abruptly attenuate leaves and a solitary syncarp with 
<taxonomicName box="[436,543,1477,1501]" class="Liliopsida" family="Pandanaceae" genus="Benstonea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Pandanales" pageId="2" pageNumber="259" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="fortuita">
<emphasis box="[436,543,1477,1501]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="259">B. fortuita</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Nevertheless, the new species can easily be discriminated from these species by the combination of characters presented in 
<tableCitation box="[559,639,1541,1565]" captionStart="Table 1" captionStartId="4.[139,191,286,305]" captionTargetBox="[147,1473,363,702]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="Table 1. – Key morphological differences between Benstonea fortuita Callm &amp; Buerki, B. glaucophylla (Ridl.) Callm. &amp; Buerki, B. parva (Ridl.) Callm. &amp; Buerki, and B. undulifolia (Ridl.) Callm. &amp; Buerki." httpUri="http://table.plazi.org/id/DF5CD4FBBC09176EFF090F1FDF4CC902" pageId="2" pageNumber="259" tableUuid="DF5CD4FBBC09176EFF090F1FDF4CC902">Table 1</tableCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[139,791,1349,1949]" pageId="2" pageNumber="259">
In their phylogeny, 
<bibRefCitation author="BUERKI" box="[388,609,1573,1597]" etAl="et al." firstAuthor="BUERKI" pageId="2" pageNumber="259" pagination="211 - 223" refId="ref3548" refString="BUERKI, S., T. GALLAHER, T. BOOTH, G. BREWER, F. FOREST, J. T. PEREIRA &amp; M. W. CALLMANDER (2016). Biogeography and evolution of the screw-pine genus Benstonea Callm &amp; Buerki (Pandanaceae). Candollea 71: 211 - 223. DOI: http: // dx. doi. org / 10.15553 / c 2016 v 712 a 7" type="journal article" year="2016">BUERKI et al. (2016)</bibRefCitation>
showed that the new species 
<taxonomicName box="[276,386,1605,1629]" class="Liliopsida" family="Pandanaceae" genus="Benstonea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Pandanales" pageId="2" pageNumber="259" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="fortuita">
<emphasis box="[276,386,1605,1629]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="259">B. fortuita</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
belongs to clade I together with the endemic Bornean 
<taxonomicName authority="(Martelli) Callm. &amp; Buerki. Although" authorityName="Callm. &amp; Buerki. Although" baseAuthorityName="Martelli" class="Liliopsida" family="Pandanaceae" genus="Benstonea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Pandanales" pageId="2" pageNumber="259" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="platystigma">
