both species have the same ecology (lowland humid forest), 
<taxonomicName box="[223,331,1701,1725]" class="Liliopsida" family="Pandanaceae" genus="Benstonea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Pandanales" pageId="2" pageNumber="259" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="fortuita">
